1
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:07,860
[A Prime Minister's Disguise]

2
00:01:08,100 --> 00:01:10,710
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:16,720
Your Majesty,

4
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,980
I have an important matter to report.

5
00:01:32,979 --> 00:01:34,910
As your uncle,

6
00:01:34,930 --> 00:01:36,430
this old bag of bones

7
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:38,479
have been toiling outside for you,

8
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:40,870
with no lack of effort,

9
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:44,950
even if there's no great merit.

10
00:01:48,030 --> 00:01:49,560
Uncle, you've worked hard.

11
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:50,590
Here,

12
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:53,560
help me share some of these.

13
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,450
Go away.

14
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:58,009
I've always been allergic to writing materials.

15
00:01:58,930 --> 00:01:59,580
Indeed.

16
00:01:59,850 --> 00:02:01,520
You just like to

17
00:02:01,550 --> 00:02:03,080
boast and drink with officials,

18
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:04,480
gamble on cockfights and dog races.

19
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,070
I do that for Your Majesty's sake,

20
00:02:06,070 --> 00:02:08,870
to implement a policy of appeasement with various vassal kings.

21
00:02:08,870 --> 00:02:10,910
I've thrown up from drinking countless times!

22
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:12,430
Forgive my frankness,

23
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:16,220
but your efforts have been generally ineffective.

24
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,070
Ineffective?

25
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:19,960
Are you trying to undermine your own uncle?

26
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:22,620
Who allowed you to take Ling'er as your consort?

27
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,590
What?

28
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:32,100
Do you object to me taking Consort Yue?

29
00:02:32,130 --> 00:02:32,630
I...

30
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,360
I remember now.

31
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:40,240
The Zheng family and the Yue family are old friends.

32
00:02:40,310 --> 00:02:41,829
Uncle, are you so angry

33
00:02:42,450 --> 00:02:45,030
because you have feelings for Consort Yue?

34
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,190
Oh my,

35
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:52,000
it's all my fault for being negligent.

36
00:02:52,070 --> 00:02:55,400
Who would have thought that the esteemed Minister Du,

37
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,590
though incompetent in state affairs,

38
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:59,360
is quite skilled in matters of the heart?

39
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,560
If you don't like her,

40
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:02,030
let her leave the palace.

41
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,000
Who has captured your heart?

42
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:08,290
Who wants to leave the palace?

43
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:12,470
Mother.

44
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:13,960
Sister,

45
00:03:14,810 --> 00:03:17,970
I was just joking with His Majesty.

46
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,710
I'm Daning's number one golden bachelor.

47
00:03:20,730 --> 00:03:22,240
In the prime of my youth,

48
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,680
I haven't thought about

49
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,079
settling down so early.

50
00:03:26,079 --> 00:03:27,079
Is that so?

51
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:29,190
Then why do you repeatedly

52
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:32,030
sabotage my arranged marriages?

53
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,680
The arranged marriage issue is a misunderstanding.

54
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:38,320
It was the minister's daughter who didn't like me.

55
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,360
Really?

56
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:41,360
Then why did that perfectly good girl

57
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:45,430
end up on Mount Wutai practicing asceticism because of you?

58
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:49,390
Your Majesty,

59
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:52,030
lend me your new bow.

60
00:03:56,310 --> 00:03:56,980
Sister.

61
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:58,030
Calm down.

62
00:03:58,730 --> 00:03:59,730
Calm down.

63
00:04:04,790 --> 00:04:07,800
Who brought these dangerous things here?

64
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,500
It's life-threatening!

65
00:04:14,190 --> 00:04:15,520
Who's talking about me?

66
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,870
Back then,

67
00:04:17,490 --> 00:04:19,029
Father sent you to the Zheng family

68
00:04:19,029 --> 00:04:21,640
to temper your unruly nature.

69
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,830
I didn't expect you to still be like this.

70
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:26,070
Now you think that as the Left Prime Minister,

71
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:27,900
running around all day,

72
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,370
I can't control you anymore?

73
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:32,680
You can.

74
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,270
Sister.

75
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,510
My sister

76
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,680
used me as a target

77
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:44,390
and even had me massage her legs for half an hour.

78
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:46,190
I really should be paid for this.

79
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:47,920
Hurry up.

80
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,800
This is a reward from His Majesty for Consort Yue.

81
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,200
We can't afford to delay.

82
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:58,120
Since I'm already in the harem,

83
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,030
why don't...

84
00:05:13,730 --> 00:05:14,530
Your Majesty,

85
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:17,470
Minister Du has gone towards Fengluan Palace.

86
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:21,550
The situation is at a stalemate.

87
00:05:21,630 --> 00:05:24,100
I'll have to rely on my cunning uncle

88
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,450
to stir up some trouble.

89
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,680
It's been so many days.

90
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,930
Why haven't I seen any meat?

91
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:38,270
His Majesty has been coming to Fengluan Palace lately.

92
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,159
The kitchen has been

93
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:41,040
cooking according to His Majesty's taste.

94
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,390
His Majesty is a martial artist,

95
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:44,050
very disciplined in his diet,

96
00:05:44,060 --> 00:05:45,800
preferring light and plain food.

97
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,240
He can be disciplined if he wants,

98
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,560
but why torment me?

99
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:49,780
Never mind.

100
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,390
Sit down and eat with me.

101
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:52,790
That won't be necessary.

102
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:55,930
I, a lowly servant, prefer heavy, meaty dishes.

103
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,480
The kitchen has made pork knuckles.

104
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,360
I won't enjoy this feast with Your Highness.

105
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,620
I'll take my leave now.

106
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,670
Where's my pork knuckle?

107
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,790
Who stole my pork knuckle?

108
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,570
Huo Jingheng

109
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,070
is really despicable.

110
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,870
I didn't even die in the Former Ning.

111
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:19,670
How could I starve to death here?

112
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:23,040
It's stewed so tender.

113
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:27,000
She was like a little snowball when she's young.

114
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,000
It's only been a few years since we last met.

115
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,800
How come she's become so robust?

116
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,330
Why is Du Tianzhao here?

117
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:46,430
You're Consort Yue?

118
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,650
Minister Du,

119
00:06:48,190 --> 00:06:49,920
although your status is noble,

120
00:06:49,930 --> 00:06:53,220
it's not appropriate to stare at me like this.

121
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,750
How come I remember

122
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:57,560
you used to be petite?

123
00:06:57,580 --> 00:06:59,040
That was when I was a child.

124
00:06:59,130 --> 00:07:00,800
Am I not allowed to grow?

125
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,600
How come I also remember

126
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:04,390
you didn't like greasy food?

127
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,720
Well, preferences

128
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,370
can change anytime.

129
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:11,750
The Yue and Zheng families are close.

130
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:13,750
It's a dark and windy night.

131
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:17,150
Why don't the two of us catch up?

132
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,260
Catch up?

133
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:22,200
I'll beat you to death.

134
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,630
What catching up?

135
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,360
You're wearing this graceful women's clothing.

136
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,390
Shouldn't you act more ladylike?

137
00:07:26,390 --> 00:07:27,390
Yue Chi.

138
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:29,350
To hell with being ladylike!

139
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,160
Tell me honestly,

140
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,480
why did you sneak into the palace?

141
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,920
If you don't confess,

142
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:36,040
I'll expose this matter.

143
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:40,560
A Prime Minister taking his sister's place in marriage,

144
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,000
cross-dressing as a woman

145
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,140
and deceiving His Majesty?

146
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:46,190
Even storytellers wouldn't dare to make up such a tale.

147
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:47,840
Shut up, will you?

148
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,600
I've confessed everything.

149
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,120
What are you up to?

150
00:07:52,140 --> 00:07:53,140
Spill it already.

151
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:56,659
My nephew wants me to take on so many memorials.

152
00:07:56,659 --> 00:07:57,860
How can I manage that?

153
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:00,920
Now, a bachelor Prime Minister

154
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,590
meets a fallen politician.

155
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:04,900
It's like a ruffian meeting a rich man;

156
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,960
a fat duck has walked in the door.

157
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:09,090
It would be a pity not to take a bite.

158
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:12,220
Put away that greedy look in your eyes.

159
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:14,560
I can tell

160
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,450
exactly what you're thinking.

161
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,400
Yue Chi,

162
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:18,830
no,

163
00:08:20,310 --> 00:08:21,440
Prime Minister Yue,

164
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:23,120
let's make a deal.

165
00:08:23,510 --> 00:08:24,640
It's a give and take.

166
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,660
Not only will I not expose you,

167
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,950
but I can also

168
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:30,000
take good care of Ling'er outside the palace for you.

169
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,320
I guarantee she'll be treated like royalty,

170
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,049
and no one will dare to harm her.

171
00:08:34,909 --> 00:08:36,039
And the conditions?

172
00:08:41,090 --> 00:08:42,059
Your Highness.

173
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,390
This is so heavy.

174
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,740
What are all these treasures, Your Highness?

175
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:51,550
It's so heavy.

176
00:08:51,570 --> 00:08:52,770
Is there any message?

177
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,080
The person who delivered it said,

178
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,240
once you open it,

179
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,380
you'll know everything.

180
00:08:57,380 --> 00:08:58,280
You may go now.

181
00:08:58,310 --> 00:08:59,440
Yes, Your Highness.

182
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,440
Memorials.

183
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,360
These are my conditions.

184
00:09:14,950 --> 00:09:16,670
I won't reveal your identity,

185
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,780
and I'll take care of Ling'er for you.

186
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,630
However,

187
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:22,150
I am overwhelmed with official duties.

188
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:24,360
Taking care of Ling'er will inevitably be distracting.

189
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,990
I specially request you to serve as the acting Prime Minister,

190
00:09:26,990 --> 00:09:28,440
to relieve my worries,

191
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,840
and to solve problems for Ning.

192
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:32,600
Du Tianzhao!

193
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,360
My Lord,

194
00:09:34,770 --> 00:09:35,800
are you alright?

195
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,170
I'm fine.

196
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:40,120
I can guess who's cursing me.

197
00:09:43,090 --> 00:09:44,560
Are my clothes wrinkled?

198
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:45,650
Check the back.

199
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:46,510
My Lord,

200
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,440
you've asked this

201
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,790
many times on the way here.

202
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:49,950
Your clothes aren't wrinkled.

203
00:09:49,950 --> 00:09:50,670
What about my hair?

204
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:51,600
Is it still neat?

205
00:09:59,620 --> 00:10:01,080
[Prince Anle's Mansion]

206
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:01,610
Alright.

207
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:02,850
You can go back now.

208
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,120
My Lady,

209
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,840
the roof leaked last night.

210
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,300
We need to repair the wall.

211
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,240
Then repair it.

212
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,490
But the money in the mansion

213
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:18,670
