214
00:10:18,670 --> 00:10:19,730
We're out of money.

215
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:21,870
When will

216
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,320
Commander return?

217
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:25,740
I wish I knew.

218
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:29,110
These past few days,

219
00:10:29,190 --> 00:10:30,380
I've been calculating accounts

220
00:10:30,380 --> 00:10:31,730
and cutting costs.

221
00:10:31,810 --> 00:10:34,030
I almost pawned my hairpins and tables.

222
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:36,810
But day after day,

223
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:38,150
money only goes out, not in.

224
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:39,870
How can this large mansion

225
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:42,850
and all its people sustain themselves?

226
00:10:44,270 --> 00:10:46,680
Fortunately, there's the money His Majesty owed us before.

227
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:47,480
Originally,

228
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,320
I thought we could rob Peter to pay Paul.

229
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,110
But unexpectedly,

230
00:10:50,110 --> 00:10:51,440
His Majesty is both

231
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,970
Peter and Paul.

232
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:54,840
His Majesty did give us money,

233
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,550
but he keeps

234
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:57,670
asking my brother for weapons every day.

235
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:58,200
Well,

236
00:10:58,200 --> 00:11:00,240
that's another big hole in our finances.

237
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,490
Look at this,

238
00:11:01,830 --> 00:11:04,110
it's leaking everywhere.

239
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,600
Don't worry, Ling'er.

240
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,630
Your help has arrived.

241
00:11:16,540 --> 00:11:17,600
Come on.

242
00:11:18,510 --> 00:11:19,750
Who are you?

243
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,340
Take a closer look.

244
00:11:22,340 --> 00:11:23,710
Don't I look familiar?

245
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:27,700
Haven't you seen me when you were little?

246
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,790
Tianzhao.

247
00:11:34,420 --> 00:11:35,510
Ling'er, stop.

248
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,030
I've already promised your brother

249
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:38,430
that I won't tell anyone.

250
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:40,910
Really?

251
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:46,080
The osmanthus pastries from Zuixiang Restaurant,

252
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,360
only sold once a month.

253
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,880
It's so hard to get these.

254
00:11:51,060 --> 00:11:52,150
Put it down.

255
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:58,960
Try some.

256
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:05,150
Yue Chi is my buddy.

257
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,960
His business is my business.

258
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,400
Your brother told me,

259
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:10,840
you should stay at my residence for a while,

260
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:13,480
until he returns triumphantly from the palace.

261
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,600
To your residence?

262
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:15,910
Yes.

263
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:18,870
If you need anything,

264
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:20,150
just let me know.

265
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,810
I'll take care of it all.

266
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:25,150
Money is no issue?

267
00:12:25,270 --> 00:12:26,360
Money is no issue.

268
00:12:28,180 --> 00:12:28,980
Alright then.

269
00:12:29,030 --> 00:12:30,830
Then I'll bring my whole family.

270
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:32,320
The whole family?

271
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,390
Come here.

272
00:12:34,180 --> 00:12:34,950
My Lady.

273
00:12:37,250 --> 00:12:38,340
It's alright.

274
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,350
Money is no issue now.

275
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,320
Someone's taking care of us.

276
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:43,630
That's great!

277
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:44,550
Thank you, Young Master.

278
00:12:44,550 --> 00:12:45,550
Thank you, Young Master.

279
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:46,670
We'll have food to eat now.

280
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:48,070
We have things to eat now.

281
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,270
That's wonderful!

282
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:50,910
Thank you, Young Master.

283
00:12:59,000 --> 00:12:59,750
Wei Zhang.

284
00:13:00,490 --> 00:13:03,180
Why wasn't Minister Du present during the discussion?

285
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:04,090
I went to invite him,

