424
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:25,040
I hope nothing bad has happened.

425
00:18:28,070 --> 00:18:28,590
Your Highness.

426
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:29,560
Wait for me here.

427
00:18:29,810 --> 00:18:31,540
I asked him to take care of them,

428
00:18:31,830 --> 00:18:33,840
