435
00:19:02,260 --> 00:19:03,860
You buy me two of everything.

436
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:05,750
Of course.

437
00:19:05,930 --> 00:19:07,920
Yue Chi is just so stingy.

438
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,590
Which of these

439
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:13,720
