440
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:16,150
and which should I play with?

441
00:19:18,440 --> 00:19:21,770
Du Tianzhao!

442
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:24,240
All these twists and turns,

443
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:27,620
