444
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:29,200
Dugu Xing,

445
00:19:30,110 --> 00:19:33,000
investigate Du Tianzhao's actions in recent years.

446
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:35,550
See if he's been paying close attention to the Yue family,

447
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:36,880
especially to Ling'er.

448
00:19:53,550 --> 00:19:53,950
Who's it?

449
00:19:53,950 --> 00:19:54,590
Go.

450
00:19:54,760 --> 00:19:55,490
Come with me.

451
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,270
Yunqing.

452
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:15,350
Yue Chi.

453
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,370
It's been two years.

454
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:21,920
Yes,

455
00:20:24,310 --> 00:20:26,570
we haven't seen each other for two years.

456
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:29,660
Yunqing,

457
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:32,470
