461
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:37,750
Aren't you the Princess?

462
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:39,240
Don't you have a way?

463
00:20:39,310 --> 00:20:40,720
Please, think of something, will you?

464
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:41,440
Ling'er,

465
00:20:42,490 --> 00:20:44,350
this matter is beyond the control

466
00:20:44,830 --> 00:20:46,240
of Yunqing or you and me.

467
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:48,550
By His Majesty's decree,

468
00:20:48,550 --> 00:20:50,070
Princess Changping,

469
00:20:50,070 --> 00:20:51,960
adorned with jade and conforming to propriety,

470
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:52,640
shall diligently

471
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:54,200
observe etiquette,

472
00:20:54,310 --> 00:20:56,310
maintain dignity and tranquility,

473
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:58,400
be respectful, virtuous, gentle, and wise.

474
00:20:58,400 --> 00:21:01,350
Hereby, she is betrothed to Prime Minister Yue Chi.

475
00:21:01,590 --> 00:21:02,830
The relevant authorities are instructed

476
00:21:02,830 --> 00:21:05,110
to select an auspicious date for the wedding.

477
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:06,640
By His Majesty's decree.

478
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,130
Prime Minister,

479
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:11,070
His Majesty has sent me

480
00:21:11,110 --> 00:21:12,980
to convey a message to you.

481
00:21:13,310 --> 00:21:14,830
