482
00:21:14,830 --> 00:21:17,360
the Yue family is now part of the royal family.

483
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:18,350
Your sister

484
00:21:18,350 --> 00:21:20,310
shall enter the palace from today on

485
00:21:20,310 --> 00:21:22,010
to accompany the princess

486
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:22,790
and await

487
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:23,750
Prime Minister Yue's

488
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:25,610
triumphant return.

489
00:21:26,330 --> 00:21:27,130
Yue Chi,

490
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:29,120
this imperial decree

491
00:21:29,750 --> 00:21:30,750
is not a shackle

492
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,030
but a promise.

493
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,200
If you win,

494
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:36,930
I'll be by your side to receive honors.

495
00:21:36,990 --> 00:21:37,920
If you lose,

496
00:21:39,630 --> 00:21:41,360
I'll go to battle in your place.

497
00:21:42,490 --> 00:21:44,550
Whether it's Ling'er or anyone else,

498
00:21:45,490 --> 00:21:47,250
as long as I remain a princess,

499
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:50,110
no one can touch them.

500
00:21:52,290 --> 00:21:54,070
The army is ready to march.

501
00:21:55,130 --> 00:21:56,430
Dayan Pass!

502
00:21:59,700 --> 00:22:00,880
Huo Jingheng!

503
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:02,610
Prime Minister Yue!

504
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:04,590
As long as you're willing to surrender,

505
00:22:04,590 --> 00:22:06,070
when I restore the glory of Ning,

506
00:22:06,070 --> 00:22:08,160
I'll still appoint you as the Prime Minister.

507
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:10,320
I, Yue Chi, can only fight,

508
00:22:10,350 --> 00:22:11,750
but never retreat!

509
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,620
Break through Dayan Pass!

510
00:22:20,350 --> 00:22:22,080
March straight to the capital!

511
00:22:34,300 --> 00:22:34,830
Brother.

512
00:22:36,130 --> 00:22:37,680
