517
00:22:54,280 --> 00:22:57,110
To protect me, Yunqing made me leave

518
00:22:57,490 --> 00:22:58,750
and she alone

519
00:22:59,930 --> 00:23:02,240
fought off more than a dozen soldiers.

520
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:05,790
Brother!

521
00:23:06,960 --> 00:23:07,960
What should we do?

522
00:23:08,200 --> 00:23:10,060
Back then, only Ling'er escaped.

523
00:23:10,900 --> 00:23:12,230
I was severely injured.

524
00:23:12,580 --> 00:23:14,370
When I went to look for you again,

525
00:23:14,370 --> 00:23:16,210
you had vanished without a trace.

526
00:23:16,210 --> 00:23:17,810
I thought you had already...

527
00:23:19,830 --> 00:23:20,720
Back then,

528
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:23,030
I was surrounded by more than a dozen soldiers.

529
00:23:23,030 --> 00:23:25,310
I barely escaped with my life.

530
00:23:26,790 --> 00:23:28,200
But then I heard

531
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:30,140
you had died at Dayan Pass.

532
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:34,920
For the past two years, I've been trying to avenge you,

533
00:23:35,070 --> 00:23:36,620
but I've never succeeded.

534
00:23:37,380 --> 00:23:39,310
I heard Ling'er was ordered to enter the palace,

535
00:23:39,310 --> 00:23:40,570
so I came to rescue her.

536
00:23:40,780 --> 00:23:41,490
But...

537
00:23:42,500 --> 00:23:44,110
What's really going on here?

538
00:23:50,590 --> 00:23:51,390
Your Majesty,

539
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:52,960
the female assassin who has tried to kill you several times

540
00:23:52,960 --> 00:23:54,210
has come again.

541
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:58,550
Didn't I tell you to transport her to the border?

542
00:23:58,550 --> 00:23:59,640
Why has she returned so soon?

543
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:01,490
She escaped when leaving the capital.

544
00:24:01,490 --> 00:24:03,040
She's truly persistent.

545
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:04,510
But it's strange.

546
00:24:04,510 --> 00:24:06,640
This time she didn't rush to Yongqian Palace.

547
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:08,440
After entering the palace, she disappeared.

548
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,460
