552
00:24:16,030 --> 00:24:17,200
Go to Fengluan Palace.

553
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,200
Pass the order down.

554
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:19,170
Except for me,

555
00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:20,700
no one is allowed to enter.

556
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:25,880
