565
00:24:39,390 --> 00:24:41,420
How could you entrust Ling'er to him?

566
00:24:41,420 --> 00:24:42,070
Come with me.

567
00:24:42,070 --> 00:24:43,670
You can't stay in this place.

568
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,060
With my identity, where can I go after

569
00:24:46,590 --> 00:24:47,790
