573
00:24:52,660 --> 00:24:54,880
But together, we can definitely do it.

574
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:57,580
Yunqing,

575
00:24:58,070 --> 00:24:59,210
as a princess,

576
00:24:59,260 --> 00:25:01,000
you have the pain of a fallen nation,

577
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:02,930
but what good would killing him do?

578
00:25:03,030 --> 00:25:04,270
The world would fall into chaos,

579
00:25:04,270 --> 00:25:05,440
and the people would suffer.

580
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:07,640
How could you and me remain unaffected?

581
00:25:08,270 --> 00:25:09,590
So, are we just going to let

582
00:25:09,590 --> 00:25:11,720
Huo Jingheng, that traitor, sit on the throne?

583
00:25:11,720 --> 00:25:13,920
Then who do you want to sit on the throne?

584
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:15,000
My father, brothers,

585
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:16,200
uncles, elders,

586
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,440
at least someone from my Jiang family,

587
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:18,870
not him, Huo Jingheng.

588
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:22,000
So how do you plan to take it back?

589
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,880
How many lives are you willing to sacrifice?

590
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:26,560
How much blood and tears will be shed?

591
00:25:26,560 --> 00:25:27,960
How many families will be destroyed?

592
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:29,560
How long will the chaos last?

593
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:32,110
You're a princess.

594
00:25:33,320 --> 00:25:34,440
I may never be able

595
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:36,170
to feel from your perspective,

596
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:39,450
but I cannot agree with you,

597
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:41,880
nor will I help you.

598
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:43,400
Yue Chi.

599
00:25:44,040 --> 00:25:45,840
I served in the previous dynasty

600
00:25:46,230 --> 00:25:47,360
as a minister and an official.

601
00:25:47,360 --> 00:25:48,350
It wasn't to gain power

602
00:25:48,350 --> 00:25:49,750
and have people bow to me.

603
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:52,740
I'd rather be a dog in peaceful times

604
00:25:52,740 --> 00:25:54,270
than a man in chaotic times.

605
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:57,140
If everyone in the world could live in peace,

606
00:25:58,240 --> 00:26:00,900
I'd be content to be one among the common people.

607
00:26:05,390 --> 00:26:07,600
It's not that I'm biased towards Huo Jingheng.

608
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:08,900
Since I entered the palace,

609
00:26:08,900 --> 00:26:10,760
I've been observing him closely.

610
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:12,570
He's diligent in governance and benevolent,

611
00:26:12,570 --> 00:26:13,920
wholeheartedly serving the people.

612
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:15,070
He is a wise ruler.

613
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,790
For me,

614
00:26:17,590 --> 00:26:19,160
as long as it's a wise ruler

615
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:20,550
sitting on the dragon throne,

616
00:26:20,550 --> 00:26:22,880
whether it's Huo Jingheng or anyone else,

617
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:25,050
it makes no difference.

618
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:32,690
Who's there?

619
00:26:33,030 --> 00:26:33,720
It's me.

620
00:26:36,490 --> 00:26:38,490
Your Majesty, please wait a moment.

621
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:43,790
Then I'll just let myself in.

622
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:49,980
Why aren't you coming out to greet me?

623
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:52,610
I'm busy, Your Majesty.

624
00:26:53,280 --> 00:26:54,680
Do you need any help?

625
00:27:00,970 --> 00:27:02,640
If you don't show yourself,

626
00:27:03,300 --> 00:27:04,720
I'll come in.

627
00:27:08,350 --> 00:27:10,810
Your Majesty, are you really in such a hurry?

628
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:14,030
Are you really alright?

629
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:16,420
Besides Your Majesty,

630
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:19,260
I'm afraid no one else would dare harm me.

631
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:29,400
I've prepared some new amusements,

632
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:31,660
and was just about to present them to you.

633
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:36,610
I knew you were hiding something good.

634
00:27:37,750 --> 00:27:39,000
Are they there?

635
00:27:48,970 --> 00:27:51,100
That assassin from the former dynasty

636
00:27:51,310 --> 00:27:53,440
must be an old acquaintance of Yue Chi.

637
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:55,560
So afraid of being discovered by me.

638
00:28:02,270 --> 00:28:02,990
My dear,

639
00:28:05,880 --> 00:28:08,440
this is my memorial.

640
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:10,410
How did it end up with you?

641
00:28:10,410 --> 00:28:11,790
[Reporting:
Lady Liu Jinfeng is gentle and virtuous in nature. I sincerely hope that Your Majesty will bestow upon her the title of Empress.]

642
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:13,520
Your Majesty must have forgotten,

643
00:28:13,520 --> 00:28:15,040
you left it with me

644
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:16,400
a few days ago.

645
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:17,720
Is that so?

646
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:19,070
Yes.

647
00:28:20,110 --> 00:28:22,710
I don't have the habit of folding page corners.

648
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,480
You've read it, haven't you?

649
00:28:26,790 --> 00:28:28,440
Didn't you tell me yourself

650
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:31,740
that the harem should not interfere with politics?

651
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,070
Your Majesty's words

652
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,880
have frightened me.

653
00:28:36,700 --> 00:28:39,110
My brother used to read memorials all the time.

654
00:28:39,110 --> 00:28:40,790
I was just curious,

655
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:43,240
so I took a glance

656
00:28:43,630 --> 00:28:45,350
while organizing them.

657
00:28:47,790 --> 00:28:48,590
Your Majesty,

658
00:28:50,440 --> 00:28:52,640
are you going to punish me for this?

659
00:28:53,100 --> 00:28:54,240
Indeed.

660
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:56,400
Your Yue family

661
00:28:57,240 --> 00:28:59,500
all have the ambition of soaring eagles.

662
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:01,680
Keeping you confined in this harem

663
00:29:02,570 --> 00:29:04,170
must be frustrating for you.

664
00:29:08,970 --> 00:29:10,350
Feel free to read it.

665
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:12,610
If it can alleviate your boredom,

666
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:13,390
that's fine.

667
00:29:15,830 --> 00:29:16,570
It's a pity.

668
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:18,850
I'm afraid I'm too dull

669
00:29:18,880 --> 00:29:20,880
to find anything interesting here.

670
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:22,000
However, I did find

671
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,750
a few weapons quite intriguing.

672
00:29:23,750 --> 00:29:24,750
Your Majesty, why don't you

673
00:29:24,750 --> 00:29:26,400
accompany me to take a look?

674
00:29:26,810 --> 00:29:27,470
Certainly.

675
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:40,090
You...

676
00:29:40,090 --> 00:29:41,510
Wait.

677
00:29:42,230 --> 00:29:43,040
You could...

678
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:45,580
have sent the memorials with a servant.

679
00:29:45,580 --> 00:29:47,820
Why did you have to make me come all the way here

680
00:29:47,820 --> 00:29:49,910
and meet in such a secretive place?

681
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,510
There's no rush.

682
00:29:51,510 --> 00:29:53,240
I need you to do me a favor first.

683
00:29:54,780 --> 00:29:55,800
What is it?

684
00:29:56,860 --> 00:29:58,410
This person...

685
00:29:59,310 --> 00:30:00,440
looks familiar.

686
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:03,700
I seem to have seen her in your palace before.

687
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:08,400
Could she be...

688
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:11,020
the former princess, Jiang Yunqing,

689
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:13,200
who were once betrothed to you?

690
00:30:13,590 --> 00:30:13,920
Come.

691
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:14,510
Get up.

692
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:20,880
Settle her in your mansion for me

693
00:30:20,880 --> 00:30:22,280
and take good care of her.

694
00:30:23,070 --> 00:30:24,750
I am the current Left Prime Minister.

695
00:30:24,750 --> 00:30:26,610
You want me to take care of a former princess?

696
00:30:26,610 --> 00:30:27,790
How preposterous.

697
00:30:28,330 --> 00:30:29,750
If you put it that way,

698
00:30:29,750 --> 00:30:30,550
you giving so many memorials

699
00:30:30,550 --> 00:30:31,960
to a former Prime Minister

700
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:33,160
is preposterous too.

701
00:30:34,270 --> 00:30:35,730
You can't say it like that.

702
00:30:36,270 --> 00:30:37,440
Then how should I say it?

703
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:38,750
Didn't we agree?

704
00:30:38,830 --> 00:30:40,110
You protect my mission for me,

705
00:30:40,110 --> 00:30:41,550
and I protect yours for you.

706
00:30:41,550 --> 00:30:43,210
We are each other's guardian.

707
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:44,510
A gentleman's agreement

708
00:30:44,510 --> 00:30:45,510
must be kept.

709
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:46,680
Bah!

710
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:48,350
What am I supposed to keep?

711
00:30:48,350 --> 00:30:49,510
I'm not going to be your guardian.

712
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:51,040
I'm not asking for trouble.

713
00:30:53,270 --> 00:30:55,600
I'm not discussing with you, Du Tianzhao.

714
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,590
All these years, you've had people

715
00:30:59,590 --> 00:31:01,720
secretly investigating Ling'er at Yue Mansion.

716
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:04,050
I've recorded everything here in detail.

717
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:06,470
When you planned a chance encounter,

718
00:31:06,470 --> 00:31:08,530
and when you created opportunities.

719
00:31:08,820 --> 00:31:10,720
Those who know think you favor Ling'er,

720
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:11,550
but those who don't

721
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:13,030
might think you're a human trafficker.

722
00:31:13,030 --> 00:31:13,400
I...

723
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:14,070
What?

724
00:31:14,320 --> 00:31:15,790
If we can get along and honor

725
00:31:15,790 --> 00:31:17,160
this guardianship,

726
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:18,170
that would be best.

727
00:31:18,170 --> 00:31:19,510
Otherwise, if you want to make things difficult,

728
00:31:19,510 --> 00:31:20,570
this booklet would

729
00:31:20,720 --> 00:31:22,720
immediately be in Ling'er's hands,

730
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:25,210
so she could see your true face.

731
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:28,670
Take good care of her.

732
00:31:29,260 --> 00:31:31,320
I haven't agreed yet.

733
00:31:38,070 --> 00:31:39,000
Du Tianzhao!

734
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:40,030
You're treating me like a beast of burden.

735
00:31:40,030 --> 00:31:40,830
It's so heavy.

736
00:31:41,750 --> 00:31:43,810
You're the one who told me to bring it.

737
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:49,160
What kind of thing is this?

738
00:31:49,310 --> 00:31:50,310
Yue Chi.

739
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:51,920
You're really

740
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:53,750
a life-taking demon.

741
00:31:57,410 --> 00:31:58,720
It was Yue Chi who left you here.

742
00:31:58,720 --> 00:32:00,030
What good does it do to beat me up?

743
00:32:00,030 --> 00:32:01,400
Are you letting me go or not?

744
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:03,000
If you go out and are seen by others,

745
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:04,070
I won't be able to explain.

746
00:32:04,070 --> 00:32:04,680
Alright.

747
00:32:06,830 --> 00:32:07,590
Stop fighting.

748
00:32:07,590 --> 00:32:08,240
Stop...

749
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:10,440
Ling'er, run quickly.

750
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,380
This woman is crazy.

751
00:32:11,380 --> 00:32:12,430
Ling'er.

752
00:32:19,750 --> 00:32:21,000
You can leave now.

753
00:32:22,700 --> 00:32:24,110
Yunqing,

754
00:32:24,490 --> 00:32:26,510
I've missed you so much.

755
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:30,790
Alright.

756
00:32:32,380 --> 00:32:33,550
Alright.

757
00:32:33,550 --> 00:32:34,920
Is it really you?

758
00:32:35,030 --> 00:32:36,240
Silly girl,

759
00:32:36,240 --> 00:32:37,300
why are you crying?

760
00:32:37,420 --> 00:32:39,930
It's a happy thing for us to meet.

761
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:43,640
Alright.

762
00:32:45,030 --> 00:32:45,550
Ling'er,

763
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:46,640
your brother is still in the palace.

764
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:47,440
I need to go rescue him.

765
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:48,090
Wait,

766
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:49,200
Yunqing,

767
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:54,590
we haven't seen each other for so long.

768
00:32:54,590 --> 00:32:55,240
Look,

769
00:32:55,510 --> 00:32:57,070
you've lost quite a bit of weight.

770
00:32:57,070 --> 00:32:59,130
How about we eat something delicious

771
00:32:59,140 --> 00:33:00,160
and get some sleep first?

772
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:01,310
At a time like this,

773
00:33:01,310 --> 00:33:04,000
how could I possibly think about eating or sleeping?

774
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,550
Brother sent you back here.

775
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:06,930
He must have his plan.

776
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:08,360
What kind of plan is this?

777
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:10,270
You've never been able to tolerate injustice

778
00:33:10,270 --> 00:33:11,870
and you hate all those rules.

779
00:33:12,030 --> 00:33:12,630
Are you

780
00:33:12,830 --> 00:33:14,270
really going to marry Huo Jingheng

781
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:15,600
and become his consort?

782
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:20,790
What on earth are you up to?
